divs: Sighting Detailswas on our way to williamstown ky on rt22 and about halfway there saw people pointing up to the sky, as we looked up my wife and my self saw some kind of objects in the sky we just happened to have our vido camera with us and my wife tried to take a shot with the camera but she forgot to take the cover off the lens so i stoped and removed the lens and started to file what was in the sky when we first seen them they close enough to tell that they were big and just as i started to film them some jets flew over and they moved away fast so i filmed what i could. after i filmed about 2mins. i lost sight of them .i have no ideal what they were all i know is the jets were interested in them. the three objects were flying in formation like a flock of geese ( V ) they were moving slow until the jets showed up then they quickly picked up speed. My wife and I were very excited when we seen them we had never seen anything like them before. they changed cours and moved out of sight.
